{"source":"user-event","type":"click","text":"C\n    \n      Mode Morphing\n      No new screen — existing screens transform when TinkerClaw is active. Home shows agent status + recent activity instead of just a clock. Chat gets tool indicators + agent suggestions. Settings shows agent config + capabilities. The whole device feels different in agent mode.\n      \n        Think: The device shapeshifts based on what mode you're in\n        Effort: Medium-High — changes across 3 UI files\n        LVGL objects: +8-12 objects (reuses existing, swaps content)\n        Risk: Medium — conditional code in multiple files, testing across all modes","choice":"c","id":null,"timestamp":1776253889034}
